cs.DB, cs.CY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE

This paper discusses the need for traceability and provenance in medical data, which is a key concern in database systems (cs.DB). The use of workflow and provenance tracking solutions also falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques to support clinical analyses, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The adaptation of CRISTAL, a workflow and provenance tracking solution, also involves software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the management and evolution of data and workflow usage over time, which is related to the field of machine learning (cs.LG).
